# --- Secrets & PII (Highest Priority) ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/secrets.json
**/credentials.json
*.pem
*.key

# --- Local Databases (PII Risk) ---
# Since your Dockerfile installs sqlite, don't accidentally 
# ship your local test data/users to DockerHub.
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# --- Node.js & Build Artifacts ---
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log*
**/.next
**/dist
**/build
**/.cache

# --- OS & IDE Junk ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
Thumbs.db

# --- Docker & Git ---
.git
.github
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml